WEBVTT

00:00:00.992 --> 00:00:02.142
Hello.

00:00:02.651 --> 00:00:07.293
Well, I'm here to talk to you
about my animal muse:

00:00:07.317 --> 00:00:08.730
the sloth.

00:00:08.754 --> 00:00:11.220
(Laughter)

00:00:11.244 --> 00:00:15.188
I've been documenting the strange lives
of the world's slowest mammal

00:00:15.212 --> 00:00:16.800
for the last 10 years.

00:00:17.149 --> 00:00:19.863
I still remember the first time I saw one.

00:00:19.887 --> 00:00:23.984
I was fascinated by their freaky biology.

00:00:24.008 --> 00:00:27.626
I mean, what's not to love
about an animal that's born

00:00:27.650 --> 00:00:29.642
with a fixed grin on its face?

00:00:29.666 --> 00:00:31.817
(Laughter)